roughcut.media.videoeditor

Class MediaProperties

  • java.lang.Object
    • roughcut.media.videoeditor.MediaProperties

  • public class MediaProperties
extends java.lang.Object
    This class defines all properties of a media file such as supported height, aspect ratio, bitrate for export function.
